    <Folder>
      <name>每日出行路线</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>8/16 AKL 转机到 Queenstown</name>
        <description>航班+市内接驳示意；不是道路导航。 KML 连线为行程示意，实际道路请打开 Google Maps 导航。</description>
        <styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
        <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>174.7903363,-37.0065512,0 168.7434399,-45.0193000,0 168.6610000,-45.0321923,0</coordinates></LineString>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>8/17 Queenstown ↔ Coronet Peak</name>
        <description>Coronet Peak 热身滑雪；住 Queenstown CBD 最省心。 KML 连线为行程示意，实际道路请打开 Google Maps 导航。</description>
        <styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
        <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>168.6610000,-45.0321923,0 168.7388744,-44.9222017,0 168.6610000,-45.0321923,0</coordinates></LineString>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>8/18 Queenstown ↔ The Remarkables</name>
        <description>The Remarkables 滑雪；建议用官方雪场巴士或按当天道路决定。 KML 连线为行程示意，实际道路请打开 Google Maps 导航。</description>
        <styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
        <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>168.6610000,-45.0321923,0 168.8168978,-45.0549855,0 168.6610000,-45.0321923,0</coordinates></LineString>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>8/19 Queenstown → Arrowtown → Cardrona Hotel → Wānaka</name>
        <description>换城日兼观光；5 人租车更适合停留。 KML 连线为行程示意，实际道路请打开 Google Maps 导航。</description>
        <styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
        <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>168.6610000,-45.0321923,0 168.8350761,-44.9405627,0 169.0035338,-44.8815382,0 169.1364637,-44.6941691,0</coordinates></LineString>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>8/20 Wānaka ↔ Cardrona</name>
        <description>Cardrona 滑雪日；适合家庭和混合水平。 KML 连线为行程示意，实际道路请打开 Google Maps 导航。</description>
        <styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
        <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>169.1364637,-44.6941691,0 168.9497926,-44.8657038,0 169.1364637,-44.6941691,0</coordinates></LineString>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>8/21 Wānaka ↔ Treble Cone</name>
        <description>Treble Cone 滑雪日；天气/水平不稳可改 Cardrona。 KML 连线为行程示意，实际道路请打开 Google Maps 导航。</description>
        <styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
        <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>169.1364637,-44.6941691,0 168.8959500,-44.6327200,0 169.1364637,-44.6941691,0</coordinates></LineString>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>8/22 Wānaka → That Wānaka Tree / Mount Iron → Onsen → Queenstown</name>
        <description>休整+回 Queenstown；Onsen 为可选项。 KML 连线为行程示意，实际道路请打开 Google Maps 导航。</description>
        <styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
        <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>169.1364637,-44.6941691,0 169.1175644,-44.6983546,0 169.1554322,-44.6936142,0 168.6854275,-44.9809952,0 168.6610000,-45.0321923,0</coordinates></LineString>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>8/23 Queenstown ↔ Milford Sound</name>
        <description>Milford Sound 一日游示意；建议参加大巴+游船团。 KML 连线为行程示意，实际道路请打开 Google Maps 导航。</description>
        <styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
        <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>168.6610000,-45.0321923,0 167.7180530,-45.4144510,0 167.8687603,-44.6190189,0 167.7180530,-45.4144510,0 168.6610000,-45.0321923,0</coordinates></LineString>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>8/24 Queenstown → Skyline → ZQN → AKL Airport</name>
